title: Dia 5 Main Toplane/Support LF DUOQ JUNGLER
body:
Hi im ThisTrickyImp. Currently Dia5 50lp~. 
I play Toplane Tryndamere, Irelia, and Tanks mainly. Many times i fill for Support role very often: Blitzcrank, Janna, Alistar, Soraka.
Im from Austria, 21 years old, currently studying at university.

Im looking for a MAIN JUNGLER PLAT 1 to DIA 3 for (daily) duoq.
GOALS: Create early invade/counterjungling strategies; and towerdives top/botlane
Communication through skype/curse.
Requirements: English or German language. Play to climb. We cant win every game so stay calm and think rationally no matter what. if ppl flame mute them. if you flame dont apply to this post.

so yeah just add me ingame if you are interested. have a nice one.
